      "acceptanceCriteria": "Commercial CFD solver with documented V&V, configuration management, and regression test suite; achievedLevel must meet or exceed requiredLevel of 2 for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 used with vendor-supplied V&V documentation (ANSYS, Inc. QMS ISO 9001:2015). Solver regression suite executed and passed prior to study. Configuration controlled via Git-tagged release. Achieved gradation 2 confirmed."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
