      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experimental conditions replicated: flow rates 2, 3, 4, 5, 6 L/min; speed 2500 RPM; bovine blood hematocrit 30±2%. All boundary conditions traceable to published FDA dataset. Gradation 2 achieved."
