      "rationale": "Primary QOI is normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) per ASTM F1841. Secondary QOIs include area-averaged scalar shear stress and pump head-flow curve. All QOIs are directly cited in FDA guidance for CPB device pre-market submissions. Gradation 2 confirmed."
