      "rationale": "FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry used as validation surrogate; geometry similarity to commercial CPB pumps documented. Operating envelope covers clinically relevant CPB range. Validation activities judged sufficiently relevant for MRL 2 decision. Gradation 2 achieved."
