      "rationale": "k-omega SST turbulence model selected based on published benchmark performance for rotating blood pump flows. Giersiepen power-law hemolysis model used per literature consensus. Model form uncertainty not formally quantified per MRL 2 scoping. Gradation 1 accepted."
    },
