    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped to gradation 1 per the MRL 2 assessment table and are not assessed, which is acceptable. The CFD hemolysis model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device described in the claim and requirement. Regulatory submission to FDA may proceed with this credibility evidence package.",
